snippet.title: Table Tennis Touch - Official Android Trailer
snippet.description:
Woohoo! Table Tennis Touch is coming to Android (Google Play Store and Amazon AppStore on March 12th!!!)

✔︎ SUBSCRIBE ► http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...

✔︎ WEBSITE ► http://tabletennistouch.com
✔︎ FACEBOOK ► http://facebook.com/tabletennistouch
✔︎ TWITTER ► http://twitter.com/tabletennistch
✔︎ INSTAGRAM ► http://instagram.com/wiffwaffsworld

For more info on how we're getting on with Multiplayer, check out our Yakuto blog: http://yaku.to

Thankyou for all the amazing support for the game so far, and do get in touch, we're always listening!
